Class Bundle

java.lang.Object
  spas.Bundle
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBundle
public class Bundle
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBundle

A bundle of interactions that may be "compresent" at the same location in space. Bundles are intended to represent objects.

Olivier
